Outdoor and Inflatable movie screen rental company

Our Outdoor Movie Screen Rentals include everything you would need for a successful event. We utilize the best equipment the industry has to offer. Most of our outdoor movie services include screen, projection, sound, technicians and generator. We also have on hand back up equipment just in case! We so everything so you don't have to.

Outdoor Movie Screens and Inflatable Movie Screens

We use Airscreen ® inflatable outdoor movie screens for our events. This manufacturer is in the top of it's class. They easily withstand the grind of weekly rentals. These outdoor movie screens have the highest wind rating in the industry and with their design maintain a tight projection surfac for optimal viewing and professional appearance.

Outdoor Movie Projectors

The projectors we use are Christie ® brand. Falling in line with out screens they are highly regarded as the best of the best. We only project in High Definition (HD). The projectors we use for each screen carry a high level of lumens (brightness). This gives our clients the brightest, sharpest image possible - even with ambient light!

Outdoor Movie Sound

The third and equally important component to an outdoor movie event is your sound system. Each outdoor movie system is sent out with the anticipated audience size in mind. Small back yard systems to full line-arrays we ensure there isn't a bad seat in the house. We use QSC ® and JBL ® sound for all of our events. Both are trusted and of the highest professional quality.
